name: what am i worth?
description: Real-time visualization of Tezos price in USD at 5 minute intervals over the last 24 hours. Prices are represented chronologically, with the outermost circle representing the most recent price. Dark grey and white circles indicate price decreases and increases, respectively. The size of each circle corresponds to the price, normalized using the range over the last 24 hours. Original artwork by landlinesart (twitter: @landlinesart1 instagram: @at_landlinesart).
